data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_d14b7ba896af1e5e00699893278b7c81908c19f8028af6d83b","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":286,"text":"**Smart Eyewear (Contoso Galaxy Innovations – SmartView Glasses)** is a wearable glasses platform that combines AR, hands-free AI interaction, and onboard capture, while still functioning as protective eyewear. In the available documentation, Smart Eyewear includes these key features :\n\n## Core features\n- **Augmented Reality (AR) interface**: An AR layer/interface built into the glasses, intended for interactive “overlays” while you wear them.   \n- **Voice-controlled AI agent**: Hands-free control via voice commands, using an embedded AI assistant/agent experience.   \n- **HD video recording with 3D audio**: Built-in recording capabilities for capturing high-definition video along with spatial/3D audio.   \n- **UV protection and blue light filtering**: Lens protection features aimed at both UV and blue light exposure.   \n- **Wireless charging with extended battery life**: Supports wireless charging and is designed for longer runtime between charges.   \n\n## Supporting guidance (from the user documentation)\nThe documentation also indicates coverage for **product overview/controls**, **sizing & fit**, **care & maintenance**, an AR **break-in period**, **safety tips**, and **troubleshooting**—suggesting the product is meant to be worn regularly and configured for comfort and safe use. "}

